  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "chapterTitle": "第一部分 先验感性论",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26392183_12_925-954",
          "range": "925-954",
          "rangeStart": 925,
          "rangeEnd": 954,
          "markText": "通过我们被对象刺激的方式获得表象的能力（感受性）叫做感性。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749291993,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:26:33",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392183&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=925&rangeEnd=954",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0132f607192b677e018b46?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=925&rangeEnd=954"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26392183_12_1221-1295",
          "range": "1221-1295",
          "rangeStart": 1221,
          "rangeEnd": 1295,
          "markText": "如果我们被一个对象所刺激，则对象对表象能力的作用就是感觉。通过感觉与对象发生关系的那些直观就叫做经验性的。一个经验性直观的未被规定的对象就叫做显象。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749291987,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:26:27",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392183&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1221&rangeEnd=1295",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0132f607192b677e018b46?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1221&rangeEnd=1295"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "导论",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26392183_10_747-772",
          "range": "747-772",
          "rangeStart": 747,
          "rangeEnd": 772,
          "markText": "我们没有任何知识先行于经验，一切知识都从经验开始。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749291980,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:26:20",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392183&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=747&rangeEnd=772",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0132f607192b677e018b46?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=747&rangeEnd=772"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "第一版前言(1)",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26392183_8_613-702",
          "range": "613-702",
          "rangeStart": 613,
          "rangeEnd": 702,
          "markText": "人类理性在其知识的某一门类中有如下特殊的命运：它为种种问题所烦扰，却无法摆脱这些问题，因为它们是由理性自身的本性向它提出的，但它也无法回答它们，因为它们超越了人类理性的一切能力。",
          "colorStyle": 3,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749291966,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-07 18:26:06",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392183&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=613&rangeEnd=702",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0132f607192b677e018b46?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=613&rangeEnd=702"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
